    <h2>Cuti-cuti Malaysia</h2>
    <p>Interesting places to visit in Malaysia. With our package, you get to explore and wander around
        in this state that was filled with its own uniqueness and beauty.
    </p>
    
<dl>
    <h3>Sabah</h3>
    <p>4 days 3 night (RM1450 per pax)</p>
  <dt>Itinerary</dt>
<ul>
    <li>Kota Kinabalu</li>
    <ul>
        <li>Arrival in KKIA and proceed to hotel</li>
        <li>Heading to Kadazan Dusun Cultural Association (KDCA)</li>
        <li>Gaya Street Market at night</li>
        <li>Go back to hotel to rest</li>
    </ul>

    <li>Kota Kinabalu</li>
    <ul>
        <li>Pick up at hotel after breakfast</li>
        <li>Depart from Jesselton Point Ferry Terminal</li>
        <li>Island hopping in Tunku Abdul Rahman Marine Park </li>
        <li>Chilling at Tanjung Aru Beach</li>
    </ul>

    <li>Kota Kinabalu - Kundasang</li>
    <ul>
        <li>Head to Kundasang at 7 am</li>
        <li>Mesilou Highland Strawberry Farm</li>
        <li>Kinabalu Park</li>
    </ul>
    
    <li>Kundasang</li>
    <ul>
        <li>Head out for scenic mountain view in the morning</li>
        <li>Ladang Tenusu Desa Cattle</li>
        <li>Poring Hot Spring</li>
        <li>Going back to KK</li>
    </ul>
</dl>

<dl>
    <h3>Melaka</h3>
    <p>2 days 1 night (RM350 per pax)</p>
  <dt>Itinerary</dt>
<ul>
    <li>Banda Hilir</li>
    <ul>
        <li>Arrive at Melaka Sentral and proceed to hotel</li>
        <li>Head to Jonker Street and around Banda Hilir</li>
        <li>Malacca Sultanate Palace Museum</li>
    </ul>

    <li>Ayer Keroh - Kota Syahbandar</li>
    <ul>
        <li>Pick up at hotel after breakfast</li>
        <li>Malacca Zoo</li>
        <li>Encore Melaka</li>
    </ul>
</dl>

<dl>
    <h3>Langkawi Island</h3>
    <p>3 days 2 nights (RM 1200 per pax)</p>
  <dt>Itinerary</dt>
<ul>
    <li>Kuah - Cenang</li>
    <ul>
        <li>Arrive at Kuah Jetty and photo stop at Dataran Lang</li>
        <li>Proceed to hotel</li>
        <li>Head to Cenang Beach for fire show</li>
        <li>Dinner at Habak Al Sham Langkawi</li>
    </ul>

    <li>Cenang - Oriental Village</li>
    <ul>
        <li>Pick up at hotel after breakfast</li>
        <li>Underwater World Langkawi</li>
        <li>Sky Cab & Sky Bridge Langkawi</li>
    </ul>

        <li>Cenang - Oriental Village</li>
    <ul>
        <li>Pick up at hotel after breakfast</li>
        <li>Beras Terbakar</li>
        <li>Langkawi Craft Complex</li>
    </ul>
    </dl>

<dl>
    <h3>Johor</h3>
    <p>2 days 1 night (RM500 per pax)</p>
  <dt>Itinerary</dt>
<ul>
    <li>Kuah - Cenang</li>
    <ul>
        <li>Arrive at Johor Bahru Sentral and check in hotel</li>
        <li>Tanjung Piai</li>
        <li>Skyscape Johor</li>
        <li>Legoland Malaysia</li>
    </ul>

    <li>Johor Bahru - Kota Tinggi</li>
    <ul>
        <li>Pick up at hotel after breakfast</li>
        <li>Desaru Alpaca Farm</li>
        <li>Desaru Fruit Farm</li>
        <li>Kota Tinggi Firefly Park</li>
    </ul>
</dl>

